like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"噉都開post覺得自已有幾戇鳩?"},{"pid":"3e31627f939897ec811bf34f8dc0a1f47089ac68","tid":296110,"uid":3510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"冇食過組女開咩post"},{"pid":"627ea09cbfb07968b5df4c2e545b156c15178c20","tid":296110,"uid":62167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食過幾多姐女？</blockquote><br />\n克制，j但唔會食<br />\n費事搞散自己組</blockquote><br />\n渣ga <br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"5630cf9809bc1e03761e64a86ec063d9c5203cb7","tid":296110,"uid":33523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最淫亂既事係咩 食過幾多條女<br />\n<br />\n未玩過ocamp既毒撚想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見到既 camp 其實大部分時間好正經，最淫亂都係花草 game 之類，例如要組花蒙眼幫組草攞走衫上面夾仔，有啲夾喺男仔私處附近咁<br />\n<br />\n真正淫亂應該係訓覺，我聽過有組爸揀準組女落手趁訓著摸腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就唔敢喇"},{"pid":"3bea1a9a5fab84cbe6cc598f6781a2f891782ed1","tid":296110,"uid":123712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"樓主係失敗的組爸，此post已完。"},{"pid":"85fae565f357a5ed59b9e77c5209b70961c3ce8d","tid":296110,"uid":33523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>噉都開post覺得自已有幾戇鳩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔戇鳩<br />\n我見好多人擔心自己另一半去玩 camp, 諗住幫大家釋除疑慮"},{"pid":"a85a42ec5a3e734c02bdc854f66766bd177f5d37","tid":296110,"uid":33523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係失敗的組爸，此post已完。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己有女，唔洗利用組女對自己既信任咁低裝"},{"pid":"cb777087e60f60b67df418427bac9032ee2560cb","tid":296110,"uid":75500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"做得組爸都係為左食女啦<br />\n最撚憎d垃圾組爸 死狗公"},{"pid":"11358ec71ba0aa2352bca91b8997f95428f7f3b9","tid":296110,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"一個組女都食唔到樓主好失敗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2907f62871f62f957a99df1c97d00bbfaa261bf0","tid":296110,"uid":33523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個組女都食唔到樓主好失敗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對於呢一個觀點我有啲嘢想講下<br />\n<br />\n其實玩 camp 全心為食女係注定失敗<br />\n首先啲女見你咁狗公未必受落<br />\n另外個 camp 除左女仲有男，你咁樣得罪晒班男同學你黎緊幾年都冇好日子過，頂多比你攬住條女但識唔到任何朋友"},{"pid":"81edf74e257c77aadd5b37ca870f2a576166cd6d","tid":296110,"uid":33523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個組女都食唔到樓主好失敗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n據我所知，大約得三成人係透過 ocamp 出 pool<br />\n有七成人係失敗，請接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7efe0b0f6e7570291d8328e90dc2cbe0f1cd55","tid":296110,"uid":33523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"同埋我真係好少識食組女既 case<br />\n反而組老婆最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87db54990dee4363307cdfb392bbe5046c8d047","tid":296110,"uid":62282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"做組爸 好威威？做左人呀爸先講野啦"},{"pid":"d797b3cec41a16c9fa2a1015356c106e7640b72d","tid":296110,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391dbf7fbdfa27a24f284c89c37eadc26251898d","tid":296110,"uid":106554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"心態唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己都遇過好嘅組爸"},{"pid":"e399b94df6dc26b4cebe3e2a1c3544934d3ef474","tid":296110,"uid":33523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做組爸 好威威？做左人呀爸先講野啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔威<br />\n做組爸好辛苦，又要諗 game 試玩，又要出設，又要照顧組仔女，仲要出錢"},{"pid":"438c28783f98ece6b2e1cad126daa412906f9b25","tid":296110,"uid":33523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d71f80e9431d4bd267f81c43c996554f2f37cf1","tid":296110,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:12:05.000Z","msg":"關我地撚事咩，收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}